name: Get into Robotics
description:
Get into Robotics: Careers, Development, & Building Robots (for fun or profit).

Hey there robot lovers! Circuit Launch and the Hardware Collective are throwing a robo-tastic event on July 27th from 6:30 to 8:30 PM. We're bringing together a cool bunch of folks who eat, sleep, and breathe robotics. They're super pumped to share what they know about breaking into the field, building next-level tech, and the whirlwind adventure of running a robotics startup.

name: Off the Clock with Women in Robotics and InOrbit
description:
Calling all trailblazing women in the world of robotics! Join us for an exciting and empowering gathering, where we break barriers and celebrate the accomplishments of women in this dynamic field.
Off the Clock with Women in Robotics and InOrbit is a networking event aiming to foster collaboration, share knowledge, and strengthen the community of women working or interested in the field. Whether you are a student, a researcher, or a professional in the industry, this event is an excellent opportunity to meet like-minded individuals and expand your network. 
Join us and be a part of the community of women who are shaping the future of robotics!
